<p>Hey {{userName}},</p>
<p>Your order status has changed.</p>
<p>The current status is now: <strong>{{orderStatus}}</strong>.</p>
<p>Your order contains the following products:</p>
<ul>
  {{#each products}}
    <li>
      <strong>{{this.productName}}</strong> (Quantity: {{this.quantity}}, Price: ${{this.price.toFixed(2)}}, Total: ${{(this.price * this.quantity).toFixed(2)}})
    </li>
  {{/each}}
</ul>
<p>Grand Total: ${{grandTotal.toFixed(2)}}</p>
<p>If you have any questions, feel free to reach out to our support team.</p>
<p>Thank you for choosing us!</p>